metadata.name: Muse
metadata.description:
At war with my own imagination
a conflict between mimesis and genesis
an issue between the unseen and the imagined
a struggle between chaos and clarity

Lonliness as my friend
darkness as my companion
the roof as my muse
my friend, my biggest adversary

Burning deep into my bones
trapped behind the windows of my soul
is the burning flame of artistic insanity
a dire state of creative affliction, an addiction

My spirit is aware of the path to take
but my fingers too weak to follow
i long for creative freedom
a blue print in the sand of time.

Duet as a piece of art seek to highlight the journey of self discovery and self identity.
